Name: Buchae Chain: Heaven False/True VI
Desc:
This is a chain skill that shares its skill level with Buchae Chain: Heaven. After using Buchae Chain: Heaven, Hoyoung leaps forward and stomps on the enemy.
Buchae Chain: True jumps again after successfully stomping on the enemy each time.
Buchae Chain: False does not cause you to take damage even when attacking enemies in the Damage Reflection Status.
Required Skill: Buchae Chain: Heaven Lv. 20 or higher
